{"tid":2361893,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《紐時》：侵尾聲亦鞏固抗中格局，拜登或推翻決定！","createTime":"2021-01-11T05:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T06:41:54.000Z","uid":219007,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"31ff689200ca009f9ac5b86498ed7051fe00f62c","tid":2361893,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T05:24:43.000Z","msg":"《紐約時報》報道，特朗普政府試圖在任期尾聲鞏固強硬抗中格局，國務院內部有反彈聲音，即將上任的拜登政府或許會推翻這項決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210111/YZYKVTUSWJD5JANCYGDPRGCWTM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2rSczf6yJY8hUCD6NNKf1Vs6zb_ibmLLikCZKH4QquYuFpk0FG8fxk7Us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210111%2FYZYKVTUSWJD5JANCYGDPRGCWTM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2rSczf6yJY8hUCD6NNKf1Vs6zb_ibmLLikCZKH4QquYuFpk0FG8fxk7Us&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7a0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=70735f57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210111%2FYZYKVTUSWJD5JANCYGDPRGCWTM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2rSczf6yJY8hUCD6NNKf1Vs6zb_ibmLLikCZKH4QquYuFpk0FG8fxk7Us&h=d65a9c38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210111/YZYKVTUSWJD5JANCYGDPRGCWTM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2rSczf6yJY8hUCD6NNKf1Vs6zb_ibmLLikCZKH4QquYuFpk0FG8fxk7Us</a>"},{"pid":"1c604f866ff687f72534dcce92b3e2ff58f8844d","tid":2361893,"uid":219007,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T05:28:18.000Z","msg":"報道又稱，特朗普政府在任期倒數階段採取如此相對重大的措施，令部份人士不解；\b國務院部份官員曾表達反對，指取消美台交往限制是未經妥善審視就做出的決定；部份外交官對他們眼中最後關頭一連串外交動作感到沮喪，認為相關決定可以更早拍板定案。<br />\n<br />\n部份專家指出，這些動作用意是為預定20日就職的總統當選人拜登設下陷阱。如果扭轉決定，拜登將在國內付出政治代價；如果拜登政府選擇遵循，美中關係勢必會惡化。<br />\n曾任白宮國家安全會議亞洲事務資深主任、現任喬治城大學（Georgetown University）教授的麥艾文（Evan Medeiros）分析指，中國幾乎肯定會憤怒反應，但僅止於言語，不大可能在拜登就任前搞壞美中關係，而是會觀察拜登上台後怎麼處理。"},{"pid":"480f7d2eb4a601db70dc2b6ec14650fe888de157","tid":2361893,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T05:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644303fee52504d79454391d370d4277a9544ded","tid":2361893,"uid":243677,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T05:35:54.000Z","msg":"一早預撚左奶共登會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33496a814738c8a1c9d0330e4e225048230c5234","tid":2361893,"uid":100680,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T05:37:56.000Z","msg":"台灣今次慘了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ac282bfdad269b448081588925b1ce66b47d9b","tid":2361893,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T05:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d5a647e564708f4487c81b2aced528e1130c4a","tid":2361893,"uid":310700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"33496a814738c8a1c9d0330e4e225048230c5234","tid":2361893,"uid":100680,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T05:37:56.000Z","msg":"台灣今次慘了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=